author: @minji-c3s
text:
Dear Minji,

I just wanted to take a moment to express how much I truly appreciate you and everything you do. Your incredible talent and hard work shine through in every performance, captivating everyone who watches. It’s not just your voice and dance skills that amaze me; it’s the way you connect with fans on such a personal level. Your genuine warmth and charisma light up the stage, making every moment memorable. Watching you perform fills my heart with joy, and I can see the passion you have for your art in every note and every move.

I admire how dedicated you are to your craft. It’s clear that you put in countless hours of practice and effort to perfect your skills, and that commitment is so inspiring. The journey you've taken—from rigorous training to debuting with NewJeans—reflects your determination and resilience. You always seem to give your all, whether it’s in your performances, your interactions with fans, or even just in your daily life. Your ability to juggle so many responsibilities while maintaining such a positive outlook is truly remarkable. You have an incredible work ethic, and it sets a great example for everyone around you.

Your positivity is infectious. You remind us all of the joy that comes from hard work and passion. Even during tough times, you manage to keep a smile on your face, and that strength resonates deeply with so many of us. It’s comforting to know that someone as talented and genuine as you is out there, encouraging others to chase their dreams and believe in themselves. You create a sense of community among your fans, and it feels like we’re all part of something special because of your efforts.

Thank you for being such a wonderful role model. Your journey is a testament to what can be achieved through perseverance and love for what you do. You’ve not only inspired me but countless others who look up to you. It’s amazing to see how you continue to grow as an artist while staying true to yourself. The way you express your creativity, whether through music, fashion, or your personal style, is a beautiful reflection of who you are.

I can’t wait to see all the amazing things you will continue to accomplish in the future. Your growth as an artist is something I cherish, and I’m excited to be part of this journey with you. I hope you always remember that you have a devoted fan cheering you on every step of the way. Your hard work and dedication do not go unnoticed, and I love you and appreciate you more than words can express!

With all my support and admiration,
your biggest fan!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

text:
우리 뉴진스 아가들 발걸음이 점점 아티스트로서 발전해 가는 거 직관하는 중ㅎㅎ  
말초적인 자극으로 바이럴을 만들고 대중들을 중독시켜 상업적 성공을 가지는 거도 좋은 일이지만 그보다 아이들이 스스로 자존감을 가지고 남이 아니라 자신들을 위해서 삶을 만들어나가는 것이 훨씬 더 중요하고 좋은 일이라고 말해주고 싶다. 뉴진스는 아마 긴 시야로 넓은 폭을 가진 진짜 레전드들이 될 것이다. 각자 존재 자체가 이미 기획사의 단기적인 돈벌이 수단으로 만들어진 그룹이 아니기때문이다. 이게 다른 걸그룹과의 명확한 차이점이라고 생각한다. 뉴진스는 민희진이 사랑을 듬뿍 넣어 선별하고 가르치고 함께 어우러지며 탄생한 그룹이기게 정체성부터가 다르다. 난 길게 볼거다. 50살 혜인이가 4명의 언니들과 함께 무대에 설 날을 끝까지 지켜볼 것이다. 사랑해뉴~~우리 지치지 말고 천천히 가자~~
